{"tid":947031,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"兒子叫EXO粉絲「適當留言」 《逆權司機》男主角要為兒子失言道歉","createTime":"2018-12-19T03:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T16:04:03.000Z","uid":152123,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac8449996973309175ba40da813dd021c366e26","tid":947031,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-u-q2Ab_W5nA/WdS4yF3BmyI/AAAAAAAAPz0/WXG6aWkd9xMnxC0yxcitNVTPmheCArshgCLcBGAs/s1600/A%2BTaxi%2BDriver_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-u-q2Ab_W5nA%2FWdS4yF3BmyI%2FAAAAAAAAPz0%2FWXG6aWkd9xMnxC0yxcitNVTPmheCArshgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FA%252BTaxi%252BDriver_Poster.jpg&h=29746c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ejmUXB2kcjQ/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FejmUXB2kcjQ%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=ef629543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓片《逆權司機》男星宋康昊主演嘅《Drug King》將於明日喺韓國開畫，由於同日撞正人氣男團EXO成員D.O.主演嘅新片《勁舞Dancing癲》(Swing Kids)同日上映，由於《Drug King》係19禁電影，喺預售方面就以《勁舞Dancing癲》領先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dramamilk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/DO-in-Korean-Swing-Kids-Movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramamilk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FDO-in-Korean-Swing-Kids-Movie.jpg&h=096cc368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而宋康昊嘅愛兒宋俊平噚日就喺Instagram留言叫「EXO粉絲，你哋適當地留言喇。」當中宋俊平冇特別解釋指摘EXO粉絲嘅原因，外界推測係因為網上有對《Drug King》嘅惡評，從而拉低咗《Drug King》嘅評分，唔知係唔係因為咁令到宋俊平就叫EXO粉絲唔好再留惡評，不過此事卻惹來EXO粉絲及其他網民不滿，事後宋俊平都有為此喺Ig向EXO粉絲道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181218/large/1545105336_ab6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181218%2Flarge%2F1545105336_ab6d.jpg&h=d2a6e3df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宋康昊和兒子<br />\n<br />\n至於宋康昊今日喺電影訪問現場亦再就兒子留言事件道歉，並指：「兒子聽到錯誤嘅消息後，輕率地發表了留言。」同時亦為兒子失言一事道歉，對EXO嘅粉絲、影迷及亞洲粉絲表示道歉。"},{"pid":"2dc9c77e079256a3e96bafdb34f62c792bd3707c","tid":947031,"uid":221265,"like":20,"dislike":14,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"EXO-L 真惡"},{"pid":"63638404ae1493cdb3c6202b3f261474eace036e","tid":947031,"uid":195516,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"狗先鍾意泡菜Pop"},{"pid":"ee25359233038bc41a007aa6f8269a1fa849bb72","tid":947031,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"EXO?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc58a4f561df80dc0d1b7a7770a0b22d20fe8d00","tid":947031,"uid":89931,"like":13,"dislike":11,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"exo fans=狗"},{"pid":"03697eeb3923cf43f171c4bdd8ce2ca254316326","tid":947031,"uid":5921,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cc58a4f561df80dc0d1b7a7770a0b22d20fe8d00","tid":947031,"uid":89931,"like":13,"dislike":11,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"exo fans=狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"泡菜仔=狗"},{"pid":"ad6b2124914cbb602220b65b52926a88db2ea492","tid":947031,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03697eeb3923cf43f171c4bdd8ce2ca254316326","tid":947031,"uid":5921,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cc58a4f561df80dc0d1b7a7770a0b22d20fe8d00","tid":947031,"uid":89931,"like":13,"dislike":11,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"exo fans=狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"泡菜仔=狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e31e3d2fa62503bbc25921e8786e7e691e64ea","tid":947031,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"男團麻鳩煩"},{"pid":"a646fa5d976dca2864c02a1855c72f0c7fed3af8","tid":947031,"uid":106336,